column5: No matter how far I put the truck in I just can't seem to get the boat off the trailer.           lmao I got this in an e-mail.
Looks fine to me.  Did you unplug the electrical?  Maybe you left the safety straps on.
funny.  just a little more an he would have been good to go.  heh.   ..the tide comes in fast when you're not paying attention.
Poor guy has no idea of the state of his truck lol.  Hilarious.
Sweet Boat, a ole blue Boston Whaler
